推出了无法播放的乙烯基和CD的新的回收计划 - 船上有粗暴的贸易和其他英国商店https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-recycling-scheme-for-unplayable-vinyl-vinyl-and-cinyl-and-cd-launched-with-rough-trade-trade-trade-trade-trade-trade-shoth-uk-stores-board-3847196?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = new-recycling-scheme-scheme-for-for-for-vinyl-vinyl and-cd-launched-with-rough-trade-trade-trade-trade and ther-uk-uk-boardPoppy Burton Tue, 18 Mar 2025 14:11:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsRecord Store Day https://www.nme.com/?p=3847196 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="粗糙的贸易" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>塑料乙烯基记录和CD的制作可能需要数百年才能在垃圾填埋场中分解</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-recycling-scheme-for-unplayable-vinyl-and-cd-launched-with-rough-trade-and-other-uk-stores-on-board-3847196">出现了针对不可播放的乙烯基和CD的新的回收计划 - 船上的粗糙贸易和其他英国商店</a>首次出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="粗糙的贸易" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-record-shop-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Key Production Group已推出了由英国独立唱片店支持的不可玩乙烯基和CD的回收计划。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="807" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995"><b>2024年最佳专辑</b></a></li></ul><p>该计划于2020年首次发起，目的是从垃圾填埋场中拯救受损的CD和乙烯基，并将其重新利用，但大流行阻碍了其进步。现在，在世界回收日（3月18日），它再次开始了。</p><p>像Rough Trade和Ray Sister Ray这样的独立唱片商店将试用该服务，该服务接受各种乙烯基记录，CD以及其包装（无论大小或状况如何），并将负责任地回收它们。</p><p>乙烯基记录和CD由不同类型的塑料（来自聚氯乙烯基（PVC）和CD的聚碳酸酯）制成，两者均可能需要数百年的时间才能在垃圾填埋场中分解。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHTr4aySGmw/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0;