-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/eilish@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/eilish@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/eilish@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benson-boone">本森·布恩（Benson Boone）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯（Gracie Abrams）</a>是在2025年Iheartradio音乐奖上获得家庭奖杯的知名人士之一。在下面找到获奖者的完整列表。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swift-eras-tour-end-impact-3820896">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）的时代之旅结束：看看它的全球影响力</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iheartradio-music-awards-2025-taylor-swift-and-morgan-wallen-lead-nominations-3831256">今年的颁奖典礼</a>是昨晚（3月17日）在洛杉矶的杜比剧院举行的，看到无数艺术家在过去12个月中的热门单曲和专辑获得了胜利。</p><p>获奖者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> ，她在当晚获得了著名的创新者奖，并用她的演讲来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-hits-back-ageism-in-pop-im-just-getting-warmed-up-3847136">召集流行音乐行业的“年龄歧视”</a> ，并保证她只是在职业生涯中才刚刚开始。</p><p>当晚的另一个令人难忘的时刻来自本森·布恩（Benson Boone），他以巨大的热门单曲“美丽的事物”（Beautiful Themings）赢得了年度歌曲类别中的奖项。它不仅看到他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3833854">在格莱美奖中空手而归</a>后获得了奖项，而且还标志着自2021年以来的第一位男性艺术家赢得了该类别的胜利，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">《周刊》（The Weeknd）</a>以他的歌曲“盲目的灯光”（通过<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/2025-iheartradio-music-awards-winners-list-1235924293/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>广告牌</em></a>）获得了奖项。</p><p>在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">玛丽亚·凯里（Mariah Carey）</a>获得了偶像奖，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nelly">内莉（Nelly）</a>获得了地标奖，格雷西·艾布拉姆斯（Gracie Abrams）签下了突破性奖。对于后者，她用接受演讲分享了对泰勒·斯威夫特，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">诺亚·卡汉</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">民族</a>的热爱。 </p><figure id="attachment_3847143" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847143" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847143" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lady-gaga@2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga在2025年IHEARTRADIO音乐奖上获得创新者奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lady-gaga@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lady-gaga@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lady-gaga@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lady-gaga@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lady-gaga@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lady-gaga@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847143" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga在2025年Iheartradio音乐奖上获得了舞台上的创新奖。学分：凯文·冬天/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>因“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">打Hard and Hard and Soft</a> ”的年度专辑奖，击败了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a>的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">Cowboy Carter</a> ”的比赛，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3833854">他在同一类别的Grammys中输给了该国纪录</a>。</p><p>然而，当晚最大的赢家是泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）。她获得了九个奖项，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-shares-unseen-mirrorball-performance-after-winning-tour-of-the-century-prize-at-iheartradio-music-awards-2025-3847109#:~:text=Music%20Awards%202025-,Taylor%20Swift%20shar