pg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wretch-32">Wretch 32</a>宣布了一张名为“ Home？”的新专辑的详细信息。在下面查看最新的单曲“ Like Home”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/wretch-32-upon-reflection-review-2558349">Wretch 32  - “反思”评论：年度最佳英国说唱记录之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>新唱片标志着歌手，歌曲作者和说唱歌手备受期待的第六张专辑，并定于5月2日发行。</p><p>该记录将使Wretch 32冒险进行对身份和归属的深刻探索以及英国黑人的经验。它由15首歌曲组成，并从Aver Afrobeat，Grime，Dancehall和Reggae中精心融合了灵感。</p><p> “这张专辑是对黑人英国人所经历的压力，欢乐和不公正现象的有力反映，对更广泛的社会和政治景观发表了凄美的评论。”</p><p> “But more than that, the record is universal, a powerful and relatable story of place and identity, one that cuts across the many intersections of society, from hurricane Beryl that has devastated Grenada and other places in the Caribbean, the increasing widespread homelessness in Britain, refugees seeking solace from wars in countries like Ukraine, Afghanistan, Palestine, Congo, many things make people question the concept of 家。”</p><p>除了宣布LP，艺术家还分享了该项目的最新单曲。这是与Teni的新合作形式出现的，称为“像家”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="WRETCH 32-喜欢家（壮举Teni）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XpgcKvEGOuY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首单曲是从去年10月到达的主打单曲“ Black and Bristand”，看到Wretch 32与Little Simz和Benjamin AD团队合作</p><p>借助最新产品，艺术家展示了唱片的不同一面，并捕捉了剥离的节奏，有节奏的Afro-Beat Shuffle。它还与一个新的音乐视频一起，反映了歌曲中捕获的反光，宁静的能量。在上面查看。</p><p>它与唱片的总体主题联系在一起，这是Wretch 32提出了一个“在声音中讲述的世代相传的故事，涵盖了Windrush Generation的经验和试验到当今的社会，政治和音乐兴隆。”</p><p>除了新材料外，英国艺术家还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wretch-32-teams-up-with-black-music-coalition-to-launch-scholarship-for-aspiring-music-executives-3811608">与BIMM和Black Music Coalition合作</a>。在此过程中，他们推出了一项专门的奖学金，支持黑人音乐行业专业人士。 </p><figure id="attachment_3847161" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847161" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847161" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x2000.jpg" alt="wretch 32“家？”艺术品" width="2000" height="2031" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x2000-400x406.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x2000-800x812.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x2000-696x707.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x2000-1392x1414.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/wretch@2000x2000-1068x1085.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847161" class="wp-caption-text"> wretch 32“家？”艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>他在去年11月宣布合作伙伴关系时说：“音乐一直是我的生命线，并开放了一个我可能不知道的世界。”</p><p> “了解这种力量，并找到将其传递给子孙后代的方法至关重要。</p><p> <a href="https://bimm.jotform.com/Marketing/bmc-wretch32-scholarship" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>了解有关此信息的更多信息，然后<a href="https://wretch32.ffm.to/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处访问新专辑</a>。</p><p> &#39;家？&#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/wretch-32-upon-reflection-review-2558349"><em>NME</em></a>将<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/wretch-32-upon-reflection-review-2558349">在Reflection时</a>遵循Wretch的2019年专辑，并说这是“年度最佳英国说唱唱片之一”，并“证明[D]他的笔比大多数人更强大。”</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wretch-32-announces-album-home-stripped-back-single-like-home-featuring-teni-3847156">Wretch 32宣布第六张专辑“ Home？”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.co